x4freetext: Thermal neutron beam of the BR1 Reactor
GELINA of the CBNM at Geel
Three targets were used.One very thin for the 4 Pi
geometry. Two others thicker, one for the GELINA
experiment, the other for the MOL experiment
Thermal neutrons selected from a broad spectrum
Based on the mass and momentum conservation relations
the preneutron emission fission fragment mass and
energy distributions were obtained via an iterative
Errors, if present, are determined in proper Subents
Two subentries added, and two deleted: 003, 007.
and 21995011 moved to ENTRY 22650. Many REACTION
SD: INC-SOURCE was moved to Subents 002,
